  msgs: [{
    role:      <span class="str">"user"</span> | <span class="str">"assistant"</span>,
    content:   <span class="str">string</span> | <span class="str">array</span>,
    iTok:      <span class="num">number</span>,
    oTok:      <span class="num">number</span>,
    cost:      <span class="num">number</span>,
    files:     [{ name, type }],
    imageResult: { prompt, images: [{ url }] } | <span class="kw">null</span>,
    toolCalls:   [{ id, function: { name, arguments } }] | <span class="kw">null</span>,
    toolResults: <span class="str">array</span> | <span class="kw">null</span>,
  }],
  codeStore:  [[ <span class="str">"blockId"</span>, { lang, content } ]],  <span class="com">// Map entries serialised</span>
}</pre>

    <h3>Patch format</h3>
    <pre>```patch
&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt; FIND
&lt;original lines to find&gt;
====
&lt;replacement lines&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; REPLACE
```</pre>

