{
  "title": "Report Title",
  "author": "Optional Author",
  "sections": [
    {
      "heading": "Introduction",
      "body": "Paragraph text here.",
      "bullet_points": ["Point A", "Point B"]
    }
  ],
  "footer": "Page footer text"
}
```</pre>

